GBOARD GLOBAL
Usage: gboard show
&n       gboard read <number>
&n       gboard write <title>
&n       gboard remove <number>

The global board is similar in design and use to the many other
boards found on Dragon's Fang. The difference is that you can
access it from any room in the game. The usual rules apply to
the gboard, like any other board.

See also: BOARDS
