COMUNICATION
Below are listed help entries dealing with comunication
inside Dragon's Fang. Type "help <entry>" to read an
entry.

Say, Tell, Reply, Shout, Osay, Qsay, Ask, Question, 
Whisper, OOC, Mail, Recieve, Check, Auction, Sing, Knock, 
Sayto, Guild Channels, Gsay/Gtell, Psay, Obscene, Toggle.

Usage: <Channel> <message>
Example: Say Hiya!

The following channels may be Toggled off/on: 
Tell - Toggle notell
Sing - toggle song
OOC - Toggle OOC
Shout, Ask, Question, Auction, Obscene.

To turn these Channels off/on you must use the Toggle 
command. Typing it again will turn the channel back on.

Usage: Toggle <Channel>

Knock <direction> Used on closed doors to tell other 
players you wish to enter.

To use Psay correctly see phelp.
