Question Auction
Usage: question <message>
       auction <message>

These are channels reserved for specific purposes.  Messages on these
channels reach everyone who is monitoring them.  You must be at least level
three to use these channels except for Question, which is available as
soon as you have had your name authorized. 

Examples:
