#0
DREAM

Usage: dream

If you have the Dreaming skill and type this, you attempt to enter
Tel'aran'rhiod with this command.

As soon as you enter Tel'aran'rhiod, your eq that your "wake" body
has is saved to file, and you stand naked in T'A'R. A mob that takes
your appearance is put in the room where you went Dreaming, and by
waking it, others can wake you and force you out of T'A'R.

If the game crashes while you're in T'A'R, don't worry...It's all
saved as usual.

