EMOTE :

Usage: emote <message>
       : <message>

Emote is the 'standard' command used when roleplaying, to
show others what you are doing, feeling and saying.
You can use ":" instead as a shorthand.

"emote <string>" will display your name, then the string.

Example:

If your name is "Helt",

  > emote is feeling very sad today.

will display:

Helt is feeling very sad today.

See also: SOCIALS, CEMOTE, PEMOTE, POSE, LASTEMOTE
