#0
"SECOND ATTACK" "THIRD ATTACK" "FOURTH ATTACK" "FIFTH ATTACK"

Usage: Automatic.

Each of these skills works the same way - for each extra attack you have,
there is a % chance that you will get an extra attack per round for each
attack you have. You do not need an earlier attack to get a later, but
each skill only gives you one extra attack.
i.e. it is possible to have fourth attack but not second or third attack,
but you will only have two attacks per round - your normal atack and the
fourth attack.

Fifth attack is a quest-skill, but is otherwise the same as 2nd, 3rd and 4th.
