GAIN PRACTICE

Usage: Gain [weave/skillname]
       Practice [weave/skillname]

These two commands are used at the trainer.
Gain without argument gives you a list of what weaves/skills you can gain, and at what cost.
Gain with argument makes you gain that weaves/skill, if you have trains enough.

Practice without argument shows you a list of the weaves/skills you've got.
Practice with argument makes you increase that weaves/skill (up to 70%) at a practices cost.

See also: TUTOR ACHIEVE
