GET TAKE

"Get" and "take" are exactly the same and can be used interchangeably.

Usage: get | take <object>
       get | take all [object]
       get | take all all.<object>
       get | take all.<object> all.<object>

If you find something interesting on the ground, you may use 'get' to 
pick it up.  'get' can also be used to extract items from containers or
furniture.

Examples:

  > get sword corpse
  > get all corpse
  > get all all.bag
  > get all.bread all.bag
  > get bread table
  > get all table
  > get all.torch table
  
