        Fire (playername)

These two commands are only available to the nobility. When you Hire someone,
it says that that person is your (title) in his score list.
Firing that person removes that line. 
That is all it does, this is strictly for IC and rp purposes.

See also: WHO
#0
HORSETRAIN

Syntax: Horsetrain <horsename>

This skill, given to all Craftsman class players, enables them to
train player owned mounts. Morts can only train horses to a certain
level depending on what level they have themselves.
Player level   Max horsetrain level
============   ====================
   1 -  49        1
  50 -  99        2
 100 - 199        3

To see what the levels really do, type help mounts.


Note: At this point in time, horses do not exist.
