#0
LONGSLEEP "LONG SLEEP"

Usage: longsleep yes

When using this, your character will go into longsleep. When
longsleeping, you will be asleep for at least 10 RL-minutes, 
and can use no commands except channels (not question though), score
and affected. The pro's though, are that you can not be attacked
by aggreesive mobs, nor by mobs you have earlier attacked, nor
by players.  You will also not be affected by other players area
weaving in the room you are in.

See also: SLEEP WAKE
