MURDER

Usage: murder <victim>

Kill command to hit another player.  To avoid accidental flagging (i.e.
trying to type "kiss Nia" but accidentally typing "kill Nia").

Note that it is illegal to kill other players if it's not a result from 
RP. Even though, you will get the !QUIT-flag for 10 MUDHrs, in order
to prevent players to quit after an unjustified Pkilll(attempt). 
See also: FLAGS
