PROFANITY

Dragon's Fang is a public mud, and as such is open to young
and older players alike. Because of such we respectfully ask
that profanity be refrained from on public channels such as
OOC, says, guildchannels and other publicly accessible channels.
If you must curse, use the OBSCENE channel. The immortal staff
reserves the rights to take reasonable steps neccessary to stop
such behavior. In Character profanity is however encouraged in
lieu of the modern counterpart. 

See also: OBSCENE
