ACCUSE

A social used to look accusingly at someone.
#0
APPLAUD

Well...Applaud is a social making you give a round of a applause...not
much to it... *grin*
#0
BEG

A social that make you beg for money from someone...
If no target of the begging is named, you beg at the gods instead..
This is just a social, meaning you won't get any money.
#0
BLEED
A social, showing the room how much you bleed.
You won't actually lose any hp, as this is just a social, it just makes you look like you're bleeding.
#0
BLUSH

A social showing those in the room that you blush.
#0
BOUNCE

A social making you bounce around in the room.
Rather silly, but funny :).
#0
BOW

A social making you bow.
If a target is intended, you bow to him/her/it.
If you bow to yourself, you are shown to try to kiss your toes. *grin*
#0
BRB

A social showing the room that you will (B)e (R)ight (B)ack.
#0
BURP

No comments...You burp, that's all.
#0
CACKLE

A social making you cackle with insane glee. Rather useful if you're mad ;)
#0
CHUCKLE

A social making you chuckle politely.
#0
CLAP

A social that makes you clap your hands together to show your approval.
#0
COMB

A social showing that you comb your hair vainly.
You can also comb someone elses hair, but make sure he approves of it first!
#0
COMFORT

A very useful social, making you comfort someone who seems to be sad or
frustrated or whatever.
#0
COUGH

A social that gives people the impression that you are smoking too much ;)
#0
CRINGE

This social makes you cringe in terror, and if a target intended, you
cringe away from it fearfully.
#0
CRY

A social giving people in the room the impression that you cry...
If you name a targat for this social, you cry on his/her/its shoulder.
If you type 'cry me', you silently sob to yourself. Poor you.
#0
CUDDLE

A social making you cuddle someone if you name a target..Cute. :P
#0
CURSE

A social making you curse vilely for a while. You cannot curse anyone,
though...sorry.
#0
CURTSEY

This social makes you curtsey, and if a target is name, you curtsey
prettily to him/her/it.
#0
DANCE

This social makes you dance... If you name a target, it says that you
lead him/her/it to the dancefloor.
#0
DAYDREAM

This social makes you look absentminded and daydreaming.
#0
DROOL

This social makes you drool...rather yucky.
If you name a target, you drool on that person.
#0
EMBRACE

A cute social making you tenderly embrace someone.
