#0
"ADVANCED HEALING"

Usage: weave 'advanced healing' target
Duration: Instant
Basic Mana cost: 800
Cost in trains: 4
Minimum levels: Air: 25  Earth: 25  Fire: 25  Spirit: 25  Water: 25
Effect:
This weave is a more powerful version of Heal, since it restores the
targets hitpoint level to 90 %, regardless of what it had before, as
well as removes all permanent physical afflictions, such as blindness,
deafness and limps (cripple).
However, such powerful healing takes its toll, both on the weaver and
the one healed, so both get their movement points set to 0.
