#0
"DESTROY ARMOR"

Usage: Weave 'destroy armor' target
Duration: Instant
Basic mana cost: 200
Cost in trains: 2
Minimum levels: Air: 9  Earth: 23  Fire: 18  Spirit: 0  Water: 0
Effect:
Not entirely right named, this weave will destroy a piece of equipment
worn by the target, thus inflicting damage on him, as well as (hopefully)
reduce his/her armor as well. The damage inflicted on target is
(2 + (mana_add / 100) + (level / 25))d10. But, if the equipment destroyed
are located on head, or neck damage is multiplied with 3. If the equipment
is located on the body (i.e. body, waist or about) damage is multiplied
with 2. In all other cases damage is not multiplied. You can't chose which
object to destroy with this weave, it will destroy the first item possible
(i.e random :)).
#0
