"DOME OF FIRE"

Usage: weave 'dome of fire'
Duration: 5 + add/200
Basic Mana cost: 500
Cost in trains: 4
Minimum level: Air: 20, Earth: 0, Fire: 28, Spirit: 17, Water: 0
Effect:
This flammable protective weave creates a huge dome around the room,
that reacts whenever someone enters it and immerses the target
in scorching flames, inflicting 500 hitpoints of damage!
Leaving this protected room does not trigger this, though.
WARNING: If you for no reason set this ward in a room that is
frequently passed by players, you will be demoted to level 1 !!!
