Duration: 10 + your level/20
Cost in trains: 3
Minimum levels: Air: 0  Earth: 30  Fire: 0  Spirit: 0  Water: 0
Effect:
This weave creates a shield made of earth and hardened to absorb
damage. Good to have if you've lost your shield. This item cannot
be sold, but given away or donated. After the duration has expired,
the shield vanishes. It improves the wearers AC and Absorbance 
with 20 + your level/10.
