GATE

Usage: weave 'gate' roomname (old syntax)
Usage: weave 'gate' 'keyword1 keyword2 ... keywordn'

Duration: Instant/10 + add/250
Cost in trains: 5
Minimum levels: Air: 35  Earth: 35  Fire: 35  Spirit: 35  Water: 35
Effect:
This weave creates a loophole in the pattern, enabling people to go
from the room where you are to the room you created the Gate to.
It will exist in the rooms until the duration has expired or you have
entered the gate yourself. To use the gate you simply type "enter gate".
WARNING: There is a small, but still, risk of striking someone in the
target room with the Gate, killing it instantly!

This spell is gainable through rp only.
#0
