Duration: Instant
Basic Mana cost: 50
Cost in trains: 1
Minimum levels: Air: 8  Earth: 8  Fire: 8  Spirit: 8  Water: 8
Effect:
This simple travellers weave makes people refreshed, relaxes weary
muscles and infuses energy into the body, giving the target
75 + add/2 movement points.
