INVISIBILITY

Usage: weave 'invisibility'
Duration: 10 + add/100
Basic Mana cost: 100
Cost in trains: 5
Minimum levels: Air: 20  Earth: 0  Fire: 0  Spirit: 0  Water: 0
Effect:
This weave bends the light that would have hit you to instead go around
you, rendering you invisible for the duration of the weave.
There is a 1% risk that you will draw double the mana at failure.

This spell is gainable through rp only.
