#0
"PORTAL STONES"

This spell allows you to use Portal Stones to travel between different
locations in the Realms. There are two commands to use with Portal Stones, 
'list' and 'travel'

First af all, you must be grasping the One Power (or the True Power), 
secondly you must (of course) BE in a room whith a Portal Stone present.

To see which destinations you can reach with a Portal Stone, use the command
list.

Usage: list
Duration: -
Mana cost: 100

A list of destinations NEVER fails.

To travel to your destination, use the command travel. 

Usage: Travel <destination>
Duration: -
Mana cost: 200 / character

With that command, you and ALL the people in your group, will be transfered
to your chosen destination. But beware, there are two drawbacks with this.

1) It'll cost 200 mana for EVERYONE in your group, including yourself. 
   Be careful, or you might burn yourself out. 

2) If you fail with the spell, ALL your mana will be lost, actually, your mana
   will be set to -5. This can also burn out an uncareful channeler. 

Both the list and the travel command is available once you've gained
the Portal Stones spell. 

Name: Portal Stones
Usage: -
Duration: -
Mana cost: -
Cost in trains: 5
Minimum levels:  Air: 20  Earth: 20  Fire: 20  Spirit: 20  Water: 20
