#0
SLICEWEAVE "SLICE WEAVE"

This is not a weave, as the name might indicate, but a skill.
If you have this skill, you can set up a guard against any unwanted
weaves woven against you. To toggle this, type "noslice".
Whether you actually succeed in slicing the incoming weave depends
mostly on how strong you are in Fire and Spirit as compared to the
weaver's Spirit and Fire.

Beware, though; every time you automatically attempt to slice a weave,
you pay half the attacking weaves mana. You can't burn yourself out this
way, however; the weave simply bypasses the defences you've put up if your
mana is too low. Sliceweave tries to slice through -all- weaves woven by
someone else aimed at you, be they aggressive or beneficial.
#0
SLOW

Usage: weave 'slow' target
Duration: 5 + add/200
Basic mana cost: 200
Cost in trains: 3
Minimum levels: Air: 17  Earth: 16  Fire: 17  Spirit: 21  Water: 15
Effect:
This weave makes the targets muscles work slow, thus making it harder
for the target to hit or avoid getting hit during battle.
The game effects are that the targets AC is increased by 10 and hitroll
decreased by 10.
