UNBALANCE

Usage: weave 'unbalance' target
Duration: 3 + add/175
Basic mana cost: 175
Cost in trains: 2
Minimum levels: Air: 16  Earth: 15  Fire: 14  Spirit: 19  Water: 14
Effect:
This multipurpose weave worsens the target's balance considerably,
making it sit automatically when hit by the weave.
It also increases its AC by 10, decreases its hitroll by 10, and
makes it fail every attempt at bashing and tripping. Also, all
the targets attempts at backstabbing awake victims automatically fails
for the duration of the weave.
