#200
ROOMSET

Usage: roomset <flag>

This toggles the specified flag in the current room. Flags set this way are
separate from, but work the same, as the normal roomflags. These temporary
flags will not be saved.

Flag names are the same as those seen in 'stat room'
#200
HEDIT HEDITUTIL
Usages: > hedit <keyword>
        > heditutil save
        > heditutil delete <keyword>

Hedit is an online help entries editor, similar to redit, medit, oedit, etc.
Heditutil is used to either save all help entries, or delete an entry.
